description: Horizons HCN seeks to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Hang Seng High Dividend Yield Index, net of expenses, by investing primarily in the HK Underlying ETF (as defined in the Glossary). The Hang Seng High Dividend Yield Index is designed to measure the performance of Hong Kong listed equity securities characterized by high dividend yield.
name: Horizons China High Dividend Yield Index ETF
